<font color="#FF0000">ARMORED CAVALRY IN NAM</font><br>
<tt>Thu Oct 16 12:34:37 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
A new book just out - 100 MILES OF BAD ROAD - written by Dwight Birdwell and Keith Nolan. Dwight served in the 3rd squadron, 4th Cavalry, 25th IN Div for 16 months. It's a thilling accurate account  and let's the reader know how it was in the CAV. a very emotional story by a Native Amereican. The book is published by Presidio Press.<br>

